gital Repository. http://dx.doi.org/10.5061/dryad.g1qr6\",\r\n  \"doi\": \"http://dx.doi.org/10.5061/dryad.g1qr6\",\r\n  \"format\": \"wood\",\r\n  \"resources\": {\r\n    \"links\": \"zip:https://datadryad.org/stash/downloads/download_resource/25782!/WoodEtal_Append1_v2.csv\"  \r\n  },\r\n  \"location\": {\r\n    \"locality\": {\r\n      \"id\": \"GEONAMES:5873327\",\r\n      \"name\": \"Sanak Island, Alaska, USA\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"latitude\": 54.42972,\r\n    \"longitude\": -162.70889\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nfyi @mielliott an explicit example of \"stable\" doi data publications breaking due to relocated content.\r\n\r\n\r\n","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/globalbioticinteractions/globalbioticinteractions/issues/431/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/globalbioticinteractions/globalbioticinteractions/issues/431/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}